</li><li><strong>die Woche darauf </strong>the following week
</li><li><strong>keine Zeit haben </strong>to have no time
</li><li><strong>leider </strong>unfortunately
</li><li><strong>beliebt </strong>popular
</li><li><strong>die Karte </strong>the ticket
</li><li><strong>ich melde mich bei dir </strong>I will get back to you
